  "archive_policy": [
    "Prefer stable article, report, official statement, court-process, or rights-organization URLs over category pages.",
    "Do not publish unsupported allegations as fact; maintain attributed wording for investigation, indictment, and trial records.",
    "Do not enrich records with non-public child identities, private addresses, school names, family details, or exact locations.",
    "Use province or district centroids when exact public venue placement is unnecessary for accountability.",
    "Keep aggregate official statistics as context only; do not map aggregate counts as incident dots."
